{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshframework\/pushwooshgettagshandler"]},{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshframework\/pushwooshgettagshandler"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Type Alias","symbolKind":"typealias","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"PushwooshGetTagsHandler","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"PushwooshGetTagsHandler","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"typealias"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"PushwooshGetTagsHandler"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshFramework"}],"externalID":"c:PushNotificationManager.h@T@PushwooshGetTagsHandler"},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"typealias"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"PushwooshGetTagsHandler","kind":"identifier"},{"text":" = ([","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s11AnyHashableV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"AnyHashable"},{"kind":"text","text":" : "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"Any"},{"text":"]?) -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Void"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This closure is called when the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"getTags:onFailure:"},{"text":" method successfully retrieves device tags from Pushwoosh servers.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The handler receives a dictionary where keys are tag names and values are the corresponding tag values. The dictionary can contain various types including strings, numbers, booleans, dates, and arrays.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Example","level":2,"anchor":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Sync user preferences from Pushwoosh tags:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["func loadUserPreferences() {","    let successHandler: PushwooshGetTagsHandler = { tags in","        guard let tags = tags else { return }","","        if let subscriptionTier = tags[\"subscription_tier\"] as? String {","            self.userSettings.subscriptionTier = subscriptionTier","        }","","        if let favoriteCategories = tags[\"favorite_categories\"] as? [String] {","            self.userSettings.favoriteCategories = favoriteCategories","        }","","        if let notificationsEnabled = tags[\"notifications_enabled\"] as? Bool {","            self.userSettings.notificationsEnabled = notificationsEnabled","        }","","        self.refreshUI()","    }","","    let errorHandler: PushwooshErrorHandler = { error in","        self.logger.error(\"Failed to load preferences: \\(error?.localizedDescription ?? \"Unknown error\")\")","    }","","    Pushwoosh.configure.getTags(successHandler, onFailure: errorHandler)","}"],"syntax":"swift"}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Completion handler called when tags are successfully retrieved from the server."}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Related Documentation","identifiers":["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PushwooshErrorHandler","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/Pushwoosh\/getTags(_:onFailure:)"]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PushwooshGetTagsHandler"},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS/documentation/PushwooshFramework/Pushwoosh/getTags(_:onFailure:)":{"role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"getTags"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"ty